  "detailed_description": "<h1>Development Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/60c7373774ccdd3b3968730030f9a2e9.avif?t=1768548789\" width=600 height=862 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/987679fbb7ae2acb643b5d96ea2bb6a7.poster.avif?t=1768548789\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/987679fbb7ae2acb643b5d96ea2bb6a7.webm?t=1768548789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/987679fbb7ae2acb643b5d96ea2bb6a7.mp4?t=1768548789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reds are back!</strong> Their revolvers are stronger than ever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They’ve cross chained our land into <strong>Chambers</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this world torn apart by War for Booze, you’re just a guy looking for your special coffin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/622ace7c4ee135c1d9f232c0764959de.poster.avif?t=1768548789\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/622ace7c4ee135c1d9f232c0764959de.webm?t=1768548789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/622ace7c4ee135c1d9f232c0764959de.mp4?t=1768548789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story driven adventure set in open sandbox-like levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic slapstick combat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipment system with upgradeable weapons and clothing. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trading and cooking systems. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First person rolling, bullet catching, kicking, hookshot-hat, cannibalism, drinking booze and puking.</p></li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/5417826755a9af7d22a6d1441027d853.poster.avif?t=1768548789\" width=800 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/5417826755a9af7d22a6d1441027d853.webm?t=1768548789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437570/extras/5417826755a9af7d22a6d1441027d853.mp4?t=1768548789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
